हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: This heartfelt story follows a powerful CEO whose world changes when her long-lost granddaughter unexpectedly reenters her life. The narrative explores themes of family bonds, lost relationships, and the healing power of love across generations. As the grandmother and granddaughter rebuild their connection, hidden truths and emotional conflicts shape their journey toward reunion.
